      "content": "\"Reach out to the carrier? You're the logistics AI, you're supposed to have the real-time data, not just point me elsewhere. I need a straight answer. Is the shipment actually in transit right now, or is it stuck somewhere? If I find out this was held up by paperwork and you didn't tell me, there's going to be a huge issue with our account renewal. Just tell me exactly where it is. Is it currently in the local delivery network?\"",
